00:06:21,423 --> 00:06:24,017
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Right after we make friendship
bracelets and braid each other's hair.</i></b></font>

160
00:06:24,134 --> 00:06:26,557
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>For your information,
it was a magical evening.</i></b></font>

161
00:06:26,636 --> 00:06:27,808
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>But actually, I'm here
to talk about business.</i></b></font>

162
00:06:27,929 --> 00:06:29,727
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>What business?
Couture Apparel.</i></b></font>

163
00:06:29,806 --> 00:06:32,400
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Jessica and I always gave
their CEO an annual analysis</i></b></font>

164
00:06:32,475 --> 00:06:33,772
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>of their legal needs
for the upcoming year.</i></b></font>

165
00:06:33,852 --> 00:06:35,775
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And now that she's gone,
you want us to do it.</i></b></font>

166
00:06:35,896 --> 00:06:37,898
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Exactly. Sounds like
a dog-and-pony show.</i></b></font>

167
00:06:37,981 --> 00:06:40,234
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>It is more than that, Harvey.
It is a show of force.</i></b></font>

168
00:06:40,317 --> 00:06:42,194
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>For one day, Carly
Donahue needs to feel</i></b></font>

169
00:06:42,319 --> 00:06:44,242
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>like the most important
client in the portfolio.</i></b></font>

170
00:06:44,321 --> 00:06:47,791
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And having one partner go by
himself doesn't send that message.</i></b></font>

171
00:06:47,866 --> 00:06:49,243
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Louis, relax.
I'm happy to do it.</i></b></font>

172
00:06:49,326 --> 00:06:50,623
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You are?
Of course I am.</i></b></font>

173
00:06:50,702 --> 00:06:52,045
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I told you.
We're partners.</i></b></font>

174
00:06:53,288 --> 00:06:56,212
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You know, Harvey, I always
dreamed it could be like this.</i></b></font>

175
00:06:56,291 --> 00:06:58,293
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Partners, confidantes,
friends...</i></b></font>

176
00:06:58,418 --> 00:07:00,512
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I had the exact same dream, Louis.
Really?</i></b></font>

177
00:07:00,587 --> 00:07:01,759
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>No, not really.</i></b></font>

178
00:07:01,838 --> 00:07:03,431
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Does that mean you're never
going to go mudding with me?</i></b></font>

179
00:07:03,506 --> 00:07:04,786
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Yes, Louis,
that's what it means.</i></b></font>

180
00:07:06,134 --> 00:07:08,432
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I'll give Donna
the details on that meeting.</i></b></font>

181
00:07:13,016 --> 00:07:14,609
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Hey. I hope
you got a hammer,</i></b></font>

182
00:07:14,684 --> 00:07:16,311
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>'cause I just brought you
some nails.</i></b></font>

183
00:07:16,353 --> 00:07:17,855
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You found something.
Yeah, I did.</i></b></font>

184
00:07:17,938 --> 00:07:19,531
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I already found
six cases we can use,</i></b></font>

185
00:07:19,606 --> 00:07:20,903
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>and that's just
the tip of the iceberg.</i></b></font>

186
00:07:20,982 --> 00:07:24,327
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>So, let's grab our coats and go kick
Velocity's ass up and down the street.</i></b></font>

187
00:07:24,402 --> 00:07:26,951
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Easy, Tyson, you have to tell me
what kind of suits these are first.</i></b></font>

188
00:07:27,030 --> 00:07:29,954
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>They're mining suits, which means health
problems or corporate negligence.</i></b></font>

189
00:07:30,033 --> 00:07:32,035
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Either way, the damages
could be through the roof.</i></b></font>

190
00:07:32,118 --> 00:07:34,871
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Oliver, this is great.</i></b></font>

191
00:07:34,955 --> 00:07:36,127
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I know.</i></b></font>

192
00:07:37,165 --> 00:07:38,838
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And if you asked me to make an
argument about it in court,</i></b></font>

193
00:07:38,917 --> 00:07:40,464
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I'd probably shit the bed.</i></b></font>

194
00:07:40,543 --> 00:07:42,341
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>But, Mike, I'm telling you,
there's something here.</i></b></font>

195
00:07:42,420 --> 00:07:44,013
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And I'm telling you,
maybe one day</i></b></font>

196
00:07:44,089 --> 00:07:45,716
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>you'll overcome your court
stuff, maybe you won't.</i></b></font>

197
00:07:45,799 --> 00:07:48,928
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Either way, this proves that
you're a hell of a lawyer.</i></b></font>

198
00:07:50,428 --> 00:07:51,645
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Thanks, Mike.</i></b></font>

199
00:07:51,721 --> 00:07:54,816
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I've got to admit, it feels pretty
good to know I can do what I just did.</i></b></font>

200
00:07:54,891 --> 00:07:56,143
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Then why don't
you start drafting a suit?</i></b></font>

201
00:07:56,226 --> 00:07:57,478
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>'Cause after I get
these people on board,</i></b></font>

202
00:07:57,560 --> 00:08:00,188
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>that's exactly what
we're going to have to do.</i></b></font>

203
00:08:07,696 --> 00:08:10,136
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Donna, you're never going to
believe what Louis just asked me.</i></b></font>

204
00:08:10,156 --> 00:08:12,625
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Give me three guesses.
He wants to be you,</i></b></font>

205
00:08:12,701 --> 00:08:15,454
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>he wants to look like you, he wants
to wear your skin as a body suit.</i></b></font>

206
00:08:15,745 --> 00:08:17,668
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Okay. Did you just talk
without saying anything?</i></b></font>

207
00:08:17,747 --> 00:08:19,467
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>What's the big deal?
You do it all the time.</i></b></font>

208
00:08:19,541 --> 00:08:21,339
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Good one, Donna.
You're on fire today.</i></b></font>

209
00:08:21,418 --> 00:08:23,295
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Okay, what the hell
is going on here?</i></b></font>

210
00:08:23,420 --> 00:08:24,763
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Oh, you mean
The Donna?</i></b></font>

211
00:08:24,838 --> 00:08:27,387
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>It's just a little product that
Benjamin and I have been working on.</i></b></font>

212
00:08:27,465 --> 00:08:29,593
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>It doesn't have my emotional
intelligence yet,</i></b></font>

213
00:08:29,676 --> 00:08:32,036
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>but I thought I'd have a little
fun with it in the meantime.</i></b></font>

214
00:08:32,095 --> 00:08:34,348
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Do you have your emotional
intelligence yet?</i></b></font>

215
00:08:34,556 --> 00:08:36,604
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>When it can top that,
you might have something.</i></b></font>

216
00:08:39,269 --> 00:08:43,194
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Loser. Okay.
Which one of you said that?</i></b></font>

217
00:08:43,940 --> 00:08:44,987
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>She did.
She did.</i></b></font>

218
00:08:53,116 --> 00:08:54,413
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Sorry, buddy.
Grill's shut down.</i></b></font>

219
00:08:54,492 --> 00:08:55,960
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>We don't open again
till 5:00.</i></b></font>

220
00:08:56,077 --> 00:08:58,296
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>That's okay. I'm not here
for a cheeseburger.</i></b></font>

221
00:08:58,580 --> 00:09:01,254
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I'm here to talk about
Hazelton Mining Company.</i></b></font>

222
00:09:02,083 --> 00:09:03,083
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>What about it?</i></b></font>

223
00:09:03,126 --> 00:09:04,343
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You filed
a complaint alleging</i></b></font>

224
00:09:04,419 --> 00:09:07,798
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>life-threatening health
problems resulting from work.</i></b></font>

225
00:09:08,631 --> 00:09:09,974
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>That complaint
mysteriously went away</i></b></font>

226
00:09:10,050 --> 00:09:12,178
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>and I want to help you get the
compensation that you deserve.</i></b></font>

227
00:09:12,260 --> 00:09:14,308
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I don't need any help
from an ambulance chaser.</i></b></font>

228
00:09:14,429 --> 00:09:16,682
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I'm not an ambulance chaser,
Mr. Stamos.</i></b></font>

229
00:09:16,806 --> 00:09:18,023
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>My name is Mike Ross.</i></b></font>

230
00:09:18,099 --> 00:09:20,727
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I work at a clinic and our
commissions are capped at $50,000.</i></b></font>

231
00:09:20,810 --> 00:09:22,778
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>So, we are not in this
for the money.</i></b></font>

232
00:09:22,854 --> 00:09:24,071
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Then what are you
in it for?</i></b></font>

233
00:09:24,522 --> 00:09:26,490
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Let's just say
Velocity is bad news.</i></b></font>

234
00:09:26,566 --> 00:09:28,239
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Well, I'd like to help.</i></b></font>

235
00:09:29,277 --> 00:09:31,746
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>But, even if I wanted to sue
those bastards, I can't.</i></b></font>

236
00:09:31,821 --> 00:09:33,073
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I know.</i></b></font>

237
00:09:33,323 --> 00:09:35,496
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You took a payout and you signed
a non-disclosure agreement.</i></b></font>

238
00:09:35,575 --> 00:09:36,855
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>That's got nothing
to do with it.</i></b></font>

239
00:09:36,910 --> 00:09:38,833
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>They made us all
sign those things.</i></b></font>

240
00:09:39,162 --> 00:09:41,210
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>If any one of us breaks it,
it negates them all.</i></b></font>

241
00:09:41,289 --> 00:09:42,632
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Then negate them all.</i></b></font>

242
00:09:43,917 --> 00:09:45,590
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>That's easy for you
to say.</i></b></font>

243
00:09:46,586 --> 00:09:47,838
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I'm dying</i></b></font>

244
00:09:48,671 --> 00:09:49,951
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>of something
with a name so long,</i></b></font>

245
00:09:50,006 --> 00:09:52,600
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I can't even tell you
what it is.</i></b></font>

246
00:09:52,675 --> 00:09:56,145
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And you're talking about your fee being
capped at more money than they paid me.</i></b></font>

247
00:09:56,221 --> 00:09:59,441
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Listen to me. If that's really all they
paid you and you really are dying,</i></b></font>

248
00:09:59,516 --> 00:10:03,316
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>we can shatter those NDAs
in about five seconds.</i></b></font>

249
00:10:05,105 --> 00:10:06,948
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You don't understand.</i></b></font>

250
00:10:08,858 --> 00:10:11,281
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I was their supervisor,
Mr. Ross.</i></b></font>

251
00:10:11,986 --> 00:10:15,206
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I was responsible for all
those guys that got sick.</i></b></font>

252
00:10:15,698 --> 00:10:19,703
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And I'm the one that got us the
money that went with those NDAs.</i></b></font>

253
00:10:20,578 --> 00:10:22,455
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And let me guess.</i></b></font>

254
00:10:22,539 --> 00:10:25,543
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Ever since you signed them, you
haven't had a good night's sleep.</i></b></font>

255
00:10:27,877 --> 00:10:29,720
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Tell me I'm wrong,
I'll leave right now.</i></b></font>

256
00:10:34,884 --> 00:10:36,557
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>What do I have to do?</i></b></font>

257
00:10:43,977 --> 00:10:44,978
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Rachel, what are you
doing here?</i></b></font>

258
00:10:45,061 --> 00:10:46,563
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Can I come in?
Of course.</i></b></font>

259
00:10:47,230 --> 00:10:48,777
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Can I get you something?</i></b></font>

260
00:10:48,857 --> 00:10:50,859
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>No, I'm good.
Thank you.</i></b></font>

261
00:10:51,776 --> 00:10:53,778
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>If this is about checking out
the place for your wedding,</i></b></font>

262
00:10:53,862 --> 00:10:55,956
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>it might be better
during the day.</i></b></font>

263
00:10:56,030 --> 00:10:57,657
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>No, I didn't come
to talk about that.</i></b></font>

264
00:10:57,740 --> 00:10:59,492
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I came here
to talk about this.</i></b></font>

265
00:11:03,663 --> 00:11:04,789
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Rachel, this is terrific.</i></b></font>

266
00:11:04,914 --> 00:11:07,914
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You passed the character and fitness
committee without even having to go in.</i></b></font>

267
00:11:08,710 --> 00:11:10,508
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I know. Then why do you
look so concerned?</i></b></font>

268
00:11:10,587 --> 00:11:13,306
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Because I know what you and Mike
are doing to make this happen.</i></b></font>

269
00:11:13,381 --> 00:11:16,134
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Rachel, this letter has nothing
to do with what we're doing.</i></b></font>

270
00:11:16,217 --> 00:11:19,642
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You deserve this and all this guy
is doing is the right thing.</i></b></font>

271
00:11:19,721 --> 00:11:21,018
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Okay, let's say
that's true.</i></b></font>

272
00:11:21,097 --> 00:11:23,566
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>What about what you two are doing to
make the same thing happen for Mike?</i></b></font>

273
00:11:23,641 --> 00:11:25,894
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Listen. No, Harvey, I
need you to listen.</i></b></font>

274
00:11:25,977 --> 00:11:28,605
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>He just spent the past
couple months in prison,</i></b></font>

275
00:11:28,688 --> 00:11:29,780
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>and it was
supposed to be years.</i></b></font>

276
00:11:29,856 --> 00:11:31,858
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And I can't let
that happen again.</i></b></font>

277
00:11:31,941 --> 00:11:33,193
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>It's not going to
happen again.</i></b></font>

278
00:11:33,276 --> 00:11:34,796
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I know it isn't,
which is why I'm here.</i></b></font>

279
00:11:36,279 --> 00:11:39,203
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I need your word that if
things start to go south,</i></b></font>

280
00:11:39,282 --> 00:11:41,205
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>that you will pull the plug
on this whole thing.</i></b></font>

281
00:11:41,326 --> 00:11:44,125
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Rachel. Harvey, I
want your word.</i></b></font>

282
00:11:46,956 --> 00:11:48,629
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You got it.</i></b></font>

283
00:11:48,708 --> 00:11:50,676
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Things go south,
it's done.</i></b></font>

284
00:11:58,635 --> 00:12:00,228
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Hey, Mike,
you got a second?</i></b></font>

285
00:12:00,303 --> 00:12:01,475
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Yeah. What's up?</i></b></font>

286
00:12:01,554 --> 00:12:02,646
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I was hoping
you could tell me.</i></b></font>

287
00:12:02,722 --> 00:12:04,802
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Apparently, Oliver was in
the conference room all day</i></b></font>

288
00:12:04,807 --> 00:12:06,730
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>working on some case
against Velocity Data.</i></b></font>

289
00:12:07,894 --> 00:12:09,646
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Uh, yeah, I gave him
an assignment.</i></b></font>

290
00:12:09,771 --> 00:12:11,523
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>What do you mean you
gave him an assignment?</i></b></font>

291
00:12:11,606 --> 00:12:12,823
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>He had
the workers' comp case.</i></b></font>

292
00:12:13,358 --> 00:12:15,156
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I took care of that.</i></b></font>

293
00:12:15,235 --> 00:12:17,454
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Mike, your job isn't
to generate cases.</i></b></font>

294
00:12:17,528 --> 00:12:19,701
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>It's to consult on the cases
we've already taken.</i></b></font>

295
00:12:19,781 --> 00:12:21,124
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I know that.
But it's also to help</i></b></font>

296
00:12:21,199 --> 00:12:23,748
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>our associates
become better lawyers.</i></b></font>

297
00:12:23,826 --> 00:12:25,578
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Oliver got his ass kicked
in court the other day.</i></b></font>

298
00:12:25,662 --> 00:12:26,879
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I'm just helping
to build him back up.</i></b></font>

299
00:12:26,955 --> 00:12:29,424
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And there are plenty of other cases
you could have used to do that.</i></b></font>

300
00:12:29,499 --> 00:12:30,921
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Instead, you went and you
signed a class action,</i></b></font>

301
00:12:31,000 --> 00:12:32,673
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>which is something
we do not do.</i></b></font>

302
00:12:32,752 --> 00:12:34,470
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Well, why isn't it
something we do?</i></b></font>

303
00:12:34,545 --> 00:12:36,343
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>These men have life-threatening
health problems.</i></b></font>

304
00:12:36,422 --> 00:12:38,142
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>They need someone to
give a shit about them.</i></b></font>

305
00:12:38,174 --> 00:12:40,518
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>It isn't something we do because we
don't have the time or the manpower</i></b></font>

306
00:12:40,593 --> 00:12:42,186
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>to take on a giant
like Velocity.</i></b></font>

307
00:12:43,972 --> 00:12:46,896
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Nathan, I don't know
what you want me to say.</i></b></font>

308
00:12:46,975 --> 00:12:49,319
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I went out there, I signed these
guys, and they trusted me.</i></b></font>

309
00:12:49,394 --> 00:12:50,646
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I can't back out now.</i></b></font>

310
00:12:51,980 --> 00:12:54,580
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>This the kind of shit you pulled
when you were at Pearson Specter?</i></b></font>

311
00:12:55,650 --> 00:12:56,902
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>On occasion.</i></b></font>

312
00:12:56,985 --> 00:12:59,613
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Then I want you to say the next time
you think to pull something like this,</i></b></font>

313
00:12:59,696 --> 00:13:02,916
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>you have the common courtesy
to tell me before you do it.</i></b></font>

314
00:13:14,210 --> 00:13:17,464
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I suggest a warm bubble
bath and a pint of Chunky Monkey.</i></b></font>

315
00:13:17,547 --> 00:13:18,969
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Because if you're not
