549
00:22:39,942 --> 00:22:40,989
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Then why are we here?</i></b></font>

550
00:22:41,068 --> 00:22:43,287
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Because we used to
dazzle Carly with rank.</i></b></font>

551
00:22:43,404 --> 00:22:45,782
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>This year, we're going to
dazzle her with substance.</i></b></font>

552
00:22:46,448 --> 00:22:48,328
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>By knowing her business
better than anyone else.</i></b></font>

553
00:22:48,409 --> 00:22:49,410
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I'll take care
