556
00:22:56,500 --> 00:22:58,753
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>We won't let you down, Louis.
I know you won't.</i></b></font>

557
00:23:02,047 --> 00:23:03,924
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You think Jessica really
