559
00:23:10,639 --> 00:23:12,516
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Oliver, how's it going?</i></b></font>

560
00:23:14,184 --> 00:23:17,688
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>It's going okay. I'm finished
