563
00:23:24,111 --> 00:23:25,829
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>most of them did nine or 10.</i></b></font>

564
00:23:28,657 --> 00:23:30,657
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I guess that means you're
in the home stretch, huh?</i></b></font>

565
00:23:31,994 --> 00:23:33,291
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I guess I am.</i></b></font>

566
00:23:36,165 --> 00:23:39,009
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Look, Oliver, I know
what you're thinking.</i></b></font>

567
00:23:39,168 --> 00:23:41,717
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>But I was telling
Nathan the truth.</i></b></font>

568
00:23:42,379 --> 00:23:46,930
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I'm not looking to come back here with
