569
00:23:47,009 --> 00:23:48,809
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I know you don't want to
come back here, Mike.</i></b></font>

570
00:23:49,345 --> 00:23:51,973
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I guess I just wanted to say
