580
00:24:16,246 --> 00:24:17,338
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And that's why
you're going to be</i></b></font>

581
00:24:17,414 --> 00:24:19,542
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>a better lawyer
than any one of these guys.</i></b></font>

582
00:24:21,543 --> 00:24:25,264
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I'm going to go tell Harvey
