593
00:24:50,906 --> 00:24:54,331
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And it's supposed to learn
from itself, but it isn't.</i></b></font>

594
00:24:56,412 --> 00:24:57,504
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Hey.</i></b></font>

595
00:24:58,580 --> 00:25:00,207
