629
00:26:34,510 --> 00:26:36,137
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You deserve
to be a lawyer.</i></b></font>

630
00:26:36,220 --> 00:26:39,064
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You're doing good for those miners
and that's all that matters.</i></b></font>

631
00:26:39,139 --> 00:26:40,186
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I don't know, Harvey.</i></b></font>

632
00:26:40,265 --> 00:26:42,814
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>What do you care so much about
what this kid thinks, anyway?</i></b></font>

633
00:26:42,893 --> 00:26:44,645
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Because he's the reason
I decided to change my mind</i></b></font>

634
00:26:44,728 --> 00:26:46,025
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>about doing
this whole thing.</i></b></font>

635
00:26:46,647 --> 00:26:48,274
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>What do you mean?
He's a great kid.</i></b></font>

636
00:26:48,357 --> 00:26:50,826
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And he's going to
be a great lawyer.</i></b></font>

637
00:26:53,070 --> 00:26:55,414
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>But I had to watch him tank a case
without being able to help him</i></b></font>

638
00:26:55,489 --> 00:26:57,617
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>and a woman ended up
on the street.</i></b></font>

639
00:26:58,158 --> 00:27:01,412
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I thought if we do this, then
I'll never have to sit back</i></b></font>

640
00:27:01,495 --> 00:27:05,125
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>and do nothing while someone I
care about is losing ever again.</i></b></font>

641
00:27:05,207 --> 00:27:07,209
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Then stop worrying
about what we're doing.</i></b></font>

642
00:27:07,543 --> 00:27:10,012
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Because tomorrow
isn't about losing.</i></b></font>

643
00:27:10,087 --> 00:27:11,714
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>It's about winning.</i></b></font>

644
00:27:21,348 --> 00:27:23,396
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>This is ridiculous.</i></b></font>

645
00:27:23,475 --> 00:27:25,022
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>We've been up all night,
and we've got nothing.</i></b></font>

646
00:27:25,102 --> 00:27:26,479
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Yes, we do.
What is this?</i></b></font>

647
00:27:26,979 --> 00:27:29,858
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>This is the key to keeping
Carly Donahue's business.</i></b></font>

648
00:27:29,940 --> 00:27:33,069
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>How is a three-year-old interview with
Gourmand magazine going to help us?</i></b></font>

649
00:27:33,152 --> 00:27:34,529
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Because it shows
she's a foodie.</i></b></font>

650
00:27:34,611 --> 00:27:36,329
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And like Louis said,</i></b></font>

651
00:27:36,405 --> 00:27:39,079
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>we need to show her that we don't
only understand her company,</i></b></font>

652
00:27:39,158 --> 00:27:41,707
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>we understand her.
I get it.</i></b></font>

653
00:27:42,703 --> 00:27:45,422
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>What if we structured the
presentation like a nine-course meal</i></b></font>

654
00:27:45,497 --> 00:27:48,341
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>and paired a discrete piece of
legal analysis with each course?</i></b></font>

655
00:27:48,417 --> 00:27:49,669
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Like a paired
wine tasting.</i></b></font>

656
00:27:49,751 --> 00:27:52,755
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Coupled with
a paired wine tasting.</i></b></font>

657
00:27:53,922 --> 00:27:55,765
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Hold on.
Are you a foodie, too?</i></b></font>

658
00:27:55,841 --> 00:27:59,846
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>What I am is a lover of fine wine,
delightful cuisine and the ballet.</i></b></font>

659
00:27:59,928 --> 00:28:01,145
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>In any order you pick.</i></b></font>

660
00:28:01,221 --> 00:28:03,269
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Well, I don't think we
can have dancers at the meeting.</i></b></font>

661
00:28:03,348 --> 00:28:04,440
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>No, we can't.</i></b></font>

662
00:28:04,683 --> 00:28:06,105
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Which means unless
you know how to cook,</i></b></font>

663
00:28:06,185 --> 00:28:09,065
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>we need to find ourselves a world-class
chef and we need to find it fast.</i></b></font>

664
00:28:10,189 --> 00:28:11,611
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>What about this?</i></b></font>

665
00:28:11,690 --> 00:28:14,159
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Mike and I just met
with a world-class,</i></b></font>

666
00:28:14,234 --> 00:28:16,111
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>French trained chef
to cater our wedding.</i></b></font>

667
00:28:16,236 --> 00:28:18,238
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I mean, if he's available, then...
Book him.</i></b></font>

668
00:28:18,530 --> 00:28:19,747
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Well, don't you want to
hear more about his...</i></b></font>

669
00:28:19,823 --> 00:28:22,793
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Rachel, if I can't trust your taste
in pairings, I can't trust anyone's.</i></b></font>

670
00:28:23,076 --> 00:28:25,955
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>What are you talking about? I
never thanked you for this.</i></b></font>

671
00:28:26,288 --> 00:28:28,882
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>But you knew your father and
I would be a great fit.</i></b></font>

672
00:28:28,957 --> 00:28:32,461
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And if you hadn't set me up
with him after I was fired,</i></b></font>

673
00:28:33,837 --> 00:28:35,635
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I don't know
what I would have done.</i></b></font>

674
00:28:38,634 --> 00:28:40,477
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I'll book the chef.</i></b></font>

675
00:28:49,853 --> 00:28:51,373
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I assume from the fact
that you called,</i></b></font>

676
00:28:51,438 --> 00:28:52,655
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>you got
our Christmas present.</i></b></font>

677
00:28:53,065 --> 00:28:55,409
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I didn't call you.
I called Harvey Specter.</i></b></font>

678
00:28:55,484 --> 00:28:56,736
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Well, he called me.</i></b></font>

679
00:28:56,818 --> 00:28:58,616
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I wanted to come have
a little chat with you</i></b></font>

680
00:28:58,695 --> 00:29:00,242
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>before you got it
into your head</i></b></font>

681
00:29:00,322 --> 00:29:01,562
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>that you could go
behind my back</i></b></font>

682
00:29:01,573 --> 00:29:03,371
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>and cut a deal without
an admission of guilt.</i></b></font>

683
00:29:04,576 --> 00:29:05,577
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>What?</i></b></font>

684
00:29:05,661 --> 00:29:07,755
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Look, I don't give a shit
how much you offered.</i></b></font>

685
00:29:07,829 --> 00:29:09,251
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You're not going to buy
your way out of this thing</i></b></font>

686
00:29:09,331 --> 00:29:10,878
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>without telling the world
what you did.</i></b></font>

687
00:29:11,124 --> 00:29:13,564
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I don't think you understand what
the word "settlement" means.</i></b></font>

688
00:29:13,585 --> 00:29:16,054
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I understand
what it means to you.</i></b></font>

689
00:29:16,255 --> 00:29:17,347
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I just don't give a shit.</i></b></font>

690
00:29:19,716 --> 00:29:22,139
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>One hundred million. With an
admission of guilt. Sure.</i></b></font>

691
00:29:22,219 --> 00:29:23,687
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Where do I sign?
Listen to me.</i></b></font>

692
00:29:24,513 --> 00:29:27,232
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>A hundred million dollars is the biggest
payout this company's ever made.</i></b></font>

693
00:29:27,307 --> 00:29:29,275
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>No, it's not.
Because I'm not taking it.</i></b></font>

694
00:29:29,351 --> 00:29:30,443
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>What is wrong with you?</i></b></font>

695
00:29:30,519 --> 00:29:31,611
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I'm willing to cut
your clients a check</i></b></font>

696
00:29:31,687 --> 00:29:33,906
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>that will change their lives and
you're too stupid to see it.</i></b></font>

697
00:29:33,981 --> 00:29:35,107
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Here's what I see.</i></b></font>

698
00:29:35,190 --> 00:29:37,784
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Every day this case drags on, your
stock is going to take a hit.</i></b></font>

699
00:29:37,859 --> 00:29:39,611
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And every quarter
when the board meets,</i></b></font>

700
00:29:39,695 --> 00:29:41,215
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>that's going to be
their first question</i></b></font>

701
00:29:41,280 --> 00:29:43,499
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>and your biggest
goddamn headache.</i></b></font>

702
00:29:44,491 --> 00:29:46,289
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>So, the real question is,</i></b></font>

703
00:29:46,368 --> 00:29:49,998
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>"Are you ready to take responsibility
for what you did or not?"</i></b></font>

704
00:29:56,378 --> 00:29:58,972
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I see you wore your power suit
for your return to the majors.</i></b></font>

705
00:29:59,047 --> 00:30:00,390
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You're going to play
in Yankee Stadium,</i></b></font>

706
00:30:00,465 --> 00:30:01,808
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>you've got to wear
the pinstripes.</i></b></font>

707
00:30:01,883 --> 00:30:03,305
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>How did it go?</i></b></font>

708
00:30:03,385 --> 00:30:05,387
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Good. He did exactly
what we thought he would.</i></b></font>

709
00:30:05,470 --> 00:30:08,599
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Tried to lowball me, called me
an idiot and then kicked me out.</i></b></font>

710
00:30:08,682 --> 00:30:10,434
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>How high did he go?
A hundred million.</i></b></font>

711
00:30:11,768 --> 00:30:12,894
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>What?
Nothing.</i></b></font>

712
00:30:12,978 --> 00:30:14,321
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>It's just, I would have
gotten him up to two.</i></b></font>

713
00:30:14,396 --> 00:30:15,488
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And how exactly would
you have done that</i></b></font>

714
00:30:15,564 --> 00:30:16,690
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>when you told me
not to counter?</i></b></font>

715
00:30:16,773 --> 00:30:17,820
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I'm more intimidating.</i></b></font>

716
00:30:17,899 --> 00:30:20,573
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I walk into a room, people cave.
It's a gift.</i></b></font>

717
00:30:20,694 --> 00:30:22,321
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I think it's a gift
when you leave the room.</i></b></font>

718
00:30:22,404 --> 00:30:24,327
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>My gift to you
was saving your ass</i></b></font>

719
00:30:24,406 --> 00:30:27,159
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>when you screwed the pooch by
involving me in this case.</i></b></font>

720
00:30:29,745 --> 00:30:31,668
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Seriously, Harvey, I...</i></b></font>

721
00:30:31,747 --> 00:30:34,125
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I appreciate
you rolling with this thing.</i></b></font>

722
00:30:34,207 --> 00:30:36,005
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Especially when I had
to improvise.</i></b></font>

723
00:30:36,084 --> 00:30:37,084
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Don't worry about it.</i></b></font>

724
00:30:37,127 --> 00:30:40,256
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>The truth is, I like getting the
chance to work with you again.</i></b></font>

725
00:30:40,380 --> 00:30:43,179
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Besides, don't tell Rachel,
I like the added risk.</i></b></font>

726
00:30:43,258 --> 00:30:45,306
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Oh, I know.
How do you know?</i></b></font>

727
00:30:45,385 --> 00:30:48,764
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Because you told me. "Life is
like this and I like this."</i></b></font>

728
00:30:48,930 --> 00:30:51,058
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>What am I, Luke Perry?
Sometimes.</i></b></font>

729
00:30:51,266 --> 00:30:52,313
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Look, I've got to go.</i></b></font>

730
00:30:52,392 --> 00:30:54,986
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Because this asshole's going to
be back in my office in an hour</i></b></font>

731
00:30:55,062 --> 00:30:57,485
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>trying to cut a deal with
me behind your back.</i></b></font>

732
00:31:06,448 --> 00:31:07,540
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Oh, my God.</i></b></font>

733
00:31:08,909 --> 00:31:10,582
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>This is amazing.
You really think so?</i></b></font>

734
00:31:10,660 --> 00:31:14,005
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I know so. It's the perfect legal analysis
combined with the perfect presentation.</i></b></font>

735
00:31:14,122 --> 00:31:15,715
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>So, you don't think the fact
that Jessica isn't here...</i></b></font>

736
00:31:15,791 --> 00:31:18,010
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Jessica "Schmessica." Carly's
going to be blown away.</i></b></font>

737
00:31:18,085 --> 00:31:19,177
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I should promote you
both right now.</i></b></font>

738
00:31:19,252 --> 00:31:20,299
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Will you?
No.</i></b></font>

739
00:31:20,379 --> 00:31:21,972
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Worth a try.
Okay, we have some time.</i></b></font>

740
00:31:22,047 --> 00:31:23,970
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>So, I'll meet you both
back here in an hour.</i></b></font>

741
00:31:24,049 --> 00:31:25,392
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Where are you going?</i></b></font>

742
00:31:25,467 --> 00:31:26,467
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Going to go
have a prunie.</i></b></font>

743
00:31:26,510 --> 00:31:28,808
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Want to clean out the pipes
for the nine-course meal.</i></b></font>

744
00:31:32,224 --> 00:31:33,601
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Mike Ross.</i></b></font>

745
00:31:34,976 --> 00:31:36,819
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Yes?
I'm Craig Seidel.</i></b></font>

746
00:31:37,354 --> 00:31:38,981
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>What? What are you
doing here?</i></b></font>

747
00:31:39,106 --> 00:31:40,107
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I want to know
what the hell you're doing.</i></b></font>

748
00:31:40,190 --> 00:31:41,362
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>What do you mean,
"What am I doing?"</i></b></font>

749
00:31:41,441 --> 00:31:43,443
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I mean you filed 150 suits,
not just one.</i></b></font>

750
00:31:43,527 --> 00:31:45,074
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And James Palmer's going
to fight each one of them.</i></b></font>

751
00:31:45,153 --> 00:31:46,700
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Which means this thing is
going to drag on forever.</i></b></font>

752
00:31:46,780 --> 00:31:48,032
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And we're going to drop
the hammer on him</i></b></font>

753
00:31:48,115 --> 00:31:49,315
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>as soon as he gets
to Harvey's.</i></b></font>

754
00:31:49,324 --> 00:31:50,644
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Now, I don't want to
see you again</i></b></font>

755
00:31:50,659 --> 00:31:53,003
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>until I meet you for the
first time at that hearing.</i></b></font>

756
00:31:53,870 --> 00:31:55,747
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Don't you walk away
from me.</i></b></font>

757
00:31:55,831 --> 00:31:57,083
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I hired Harvey
to do a job,</i></b></font>

758
00:31:57,165 --> 00:31:58,508
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>he farmed it out to you
against my will</i></b></font>

759
00:31:58,583 --> 00:31:59,880
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>and you're going to
goddamn listen to me.</i></b></font>

760
00:31:59,960 --> 00:32:01,177
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>No, you didn't hire Harvey.</i></b></font>

761
00:32:01,253 --> 00:32:03,051
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You tried to mess
with my fiancÃ©e's life</i></b></font>

762
00:32:03,130 --> 00:32:05,007
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>and you're lucky we didn't
have you disbarred.</i></b></font>

763
00:32:05,090 --> 00:32:07,092
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>So, instead of coming to my
place of work and harassing me,</i></b></font>

764
00:32:07,175 --> 00:32:08,267
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>why don't you go back
to your hole</i></b></font>

765
00:32:08,343 --> 00:32:09,469
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>and we'll tell you
when it's done?</i></b></font>

766
00:32:09,553 --> 00:32:11,555
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Okay, but your
window's closing.</i></b></font>

767
00:32:11,638 --> 00:32:12,855
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>This thing doesn't
get wrapped up soon,</i></b></font>

768
00:32:12,931 --> 00:32:15,354
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>your shot at being
a lawyer is over.</i></b></font>

769
00:32:20,480 --> 00:32:22,073
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>If you're going to
bankroll a suit,</i></b></font>

770
00:32:22,149 --> 00:32:24,151
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>at least have the balls
to negotiate it yourself.</i></b></font>

771
00:32:24,234 --> 00:32:25,736
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I take it you didn't
like the offer.</i></b></font>

772
00:32:25,819 --> 00:32:28,197
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Admission of guilt isn't an offer.
It's suicide.</i></b></font>

773
00:32:28,738 --> 00:32:30,411
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>It's Mike Ross' case.
It's his call.</i></b></font>

774
00:32:30,490 --> 00:32:33,118
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Bullshit. Mike Ross
is some clinic worker.</i></b></font>

775
00:32:33,201 --> 00:32:34,418
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You're Harvey Specter.</i></b></font>

776
00:32:34,494 --> 00:32:35,746
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And from what
I hear about you,</i></b></font>

777
00:32:35,829 --> 00:32:37,206
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>you don't give
a shit about guilt.</i></b></font>

778
00:32:37,289 --> 00:32:39,041
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You're right, I don't.</i></b></font>

779
00:32:40,292 --> 00:32:44,547
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>So, why don't you tell me how much it's
going to take to make this go away?</i></b></font>

780
00:32:44,963 --> 00:32:47,466
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Five hundred million. Half a
billion dollars. Are you insane?</i></b></font>

781
00:32:47,549 --> 00:32:49,301
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You poisoned your employees, Mr.
Palmer.</i></b></font>

782
00:32:49,384 --> 00:32:50,761
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You're lucky
you're not in prison.</i></b></font>

783
00:32:50,844 --> 00:32:52,221
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Two hundred million.
No.</i></b></font>

784
00:32:52,304 --> 00:32:53,897
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Three hundred.
No.</i></b></font>

785
00:32:55,265 --> 00:32:56,482
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Okay.</i></b></font>

786
00:32:56,558 --> 00:32:58,686
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Make it 350
and call it a day.</i></b></font>

787
00:32:58,768 --> 00:33:00,395
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Five hundred.
Not a penny less.</i></b></font>

788
00:33:00,479 --> 00:33:01,981
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>In that case,
make it zero.</i></b></font>

789
00:33:02,230 --> 00:33:05,484
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Because you just confirmed what
I suspected since this morning.</i></b></font>

790
00:33:05,567 --> 00:33:08,195
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You picked the exact number to
make my stock take a nosedive.</i></b></font>

791
00:33:08,278 --> 00:33:10,531
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And we both know
who benefits from that.</i></b></font>

792
00:33:10,906 --> 00:33:13,079
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Craig Seidel. I don't know
what you're talking about.</i></b></font>

793
00:33:13,158 --> 00:33:14,998
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Then I guess you also
don't know that Mike Ross</i></b></font>

794
00:33:15,035 --> 00:33:16,457
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>just got an appointment
with the ethics board.</i></b></font>

795
00:33:16,536 --> 00:33:19,506
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And it's a crime
to trade this for that.</i></b></font>

796
00:33:19,581 --> 00:33:21,424
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Which means
your lawsuit is over.</i></b></font>

797
00:33:22,792 --> 00:33:24,294
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Then I'll do
something else.</i></b></font>

798
00:33:25,295 --> 00:33:28,925
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You think I won't go after you for
stealing technology from Seidel's company?</i></b></font>

799
00:33:29,007 --> 00:33:30,554
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You have no proof
I did anything.</i></b></font>

800
00:33:30,634 --> 00:33:31,760
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>No, but he does.</i></b></font>

801
00:33:31,843 --> 00:33:33,523
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And I don't give a shit
about his marriage,</i></b></font>

802
00:33:33,553 --> 00:33:34,805
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>and I'm going to
make him come forward.</i></b></font>

803
00:33:34,888 --> 00:33:37,357
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>His marriage? Is that what
he told you this is about?</i></b></font>

804
00:33:37,641 --> 00:33:39,689
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I've got news for you,
Mr. Specter.</i></b></font>

805
00:33:39,768 --> 00:33:42,988
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>The reason he hasn't come forward has
nothing to do with his marriage.</i></b></font>

806
00:33:43,313 --> 00:33:45,987
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>So, why don't you
go find out what's what?</i></b></font>

807
00:33:46,066 --> 00:33:48,034
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And I've got a feeling
when you do,</i></b></font>

808
00:33:48,109 --> 00:33:50,077
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>you'll drop this case
by morning.</i></b></font>

809
00:34:09,548 --> 00:34:10,925
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Hey-
Hey-</i></b></font>

810
00:34:11,591 --> 00:34:13,309
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You ran out of the
presentation so quickly,</i></b></font>

811
00:34:13,385 --> 00:34:14,477
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I didn't get to ask
what you thought.</i></b></font>

812
00:34:14,553 --> 00:34:15,896
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I had to get to class.</i></b></font>

813
00:34:15,971 --> 00:34:17,769
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>But I thought
it went great.</i></b></font>

814
00:34:17,847 --> 00:34:20,145
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>What about Louis?
He was over the moon.</i></b></font>

815
00:34:20,433 --> 00:34:22,106
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I'm sure he's glad
to have you back.</i></b></font>

816
00:34:22,519 --> 00:34:24,112
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I'm glad to be back.</i></b></font>

817
00:34:27,941 --> 00:34:30,694
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Well, I should, uh... What was
it like, working with my dad?</i></b></font>

818
00:34:31,403 --> 00:34:33,872
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You said it was a great pairing
and I was just wondering...</i></b></font>

819
00:34:33,947 --> 00:34:35,164
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>What you were missing.</i></b></font>

820
00:34:36,241 --> 00:34:37,242
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Yes.</i></b></font>

821
00:34:37,325 --> 00:34:41,205
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You were missing a brilliant,
tireless, sweet, funny, charming man.</i></b></font>

822
00:34:42,289 --> 00:34:45,293
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Who may also be the best
litigator I have ever seen.</i></b></font>

823
00:34:45,375 --> 00:34:47,423
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Maybe you didn't
understand my question.</i></b></font>

824
00:34:47,502 --> 00:34:51,473
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I was asking what it was like
to work with Zane, not Kaldor.</i></b></font>

825
00:34:52,048 --> 00:34:53,925
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Rachel, I'm serious.</i></b></font>

826
00:34:54,009 --> 00:34:55,727
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I learned a lot about your
father while I was there</i></b></font>

827
00:34:55,802 --> 00:34:58,225
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>and I'm telling you,
it was all good.</i></b></font>

828
00:34:58,597 --> 00:35:00,099
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>What about his temper?</i></b></font>

829
00:35:00,557 --> 00:35:02,059
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Well, maybe
it wasn't all good.</i></b></font>

830
00:35:04,185 --> 00:35:06,062
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Well, good night.</i></b></font>

831
00:35:07,606 --> 00:35:09,859
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>One more thing
I learned about him.</i></b></font>

832
00:35:11,943 --> 00:35:14,162
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>He doesn't just love you,
he respects you.</i></b></font>

833
00:35:14,571 --> 00:35:15,618
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>How would you know that...</i></b></font>

834
00:35:15,697 --> 00:35:18,416
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>When he offered you
that job, he was beaming.</i></b></font>

835
00:35:18,700 --> 00:35:21,499
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>He told everyone in the office
that his brilliant baby girl</i></b></font>

836
00:35:21,578 --> 00:35:24,878
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>was going to work for us and she was
going to blow us all to smithereens.</i></b></font>

837
00:35:28,543 --> 00:35:29,669
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>He said that?</i></b></font>

838
00:35:29,753 --> 00:35:32,723
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Rachel, I didn't tell you that
to make you feel bad.</i></b></font>

839
00:35:32,797 --> 00:35:35,220
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>He was okay that
you didn't take his offer.</i></b></font>

840
00:35:35,800 --> 00:35:37,928
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>It doesn't make me feel bad.</i></b></font>

841
00:35:39,429 --> 00:35:41,022
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>It makes me feel great.</i></b></font>

842
00:35:49,606 --> 00:35:52,029
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Is he in?
No, he had to run out.</i></b></font>

843
00:35:52,442 --> 00:35:53,989
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>All right,
do me a favor.</i></b></font>

844
00:35:54,069 --> 00:35:56,822
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Just tell him I need to talk
to him when he gets back.</i></b></font>

845
00:35:57,947 --> 00:36:00,416
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You mind if I ask
what it's about?</i></b></font>

846
00:36:01,284 --> 00:36:04,208
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I just got off the phone
with Carly Donahue.</i></b></font>

847
00:36:04,287 --> 00:36:06,039
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Louis, what happened? Rachel
said that it went great.</i></b></font>

848
00:36:06,122 --> 00:36:07,715
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I thought it did, too. But
then she called me and said</i></b></font>

849
00:36:07,791 --> 00:36:09,668
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>that the next time she asks for
a meeting with me and Harvey,</i></b></font>

850
00:36:09,751 --> 00:36:10,877
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>she better get
a goddamn meeting</i></b></font>

851
00:36:10,960 --> 00:36:12,758
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>with me and Harvey
instead of two nobodies.</i></b></font>

852
00:36:12,921 --> 00:36:14,138
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>What did you tell her?</i></b></font>

853
00:36:14,214 --> 00:36:16,216
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I told her how dare she talk
about my superstars like that.</i></b></font>

854
00:36:16,299 --> 00:36:17,346
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>She's lucky to have them.</i></b></font>

855
00:36:17,759 --> 00:36:19,306
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Louis, that's great.
Good for you.</i></b></font>

856
00:36:19,386 --> 00:36:20,433
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>She fired us, Donna.</i></b></font>

857
00:36:22,138 --> 00:36:24,687
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Oh, Louis, I'm so sorry.
Look, this isn't your fault.</i></b></font>

858
00:36:24,766 --> 00:36:26,188
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You couldn't have known.
It's okay.</i></b></font>

859
00:36:27,018 --> 00:36:28,941
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I just need to go home.</i></b></font>

860
00:36:33,525 --> 00:36:34,742
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Shit.</i></b></font>

861
00:36:34,818 --> 00:36:38,118
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>It's okay, Donna. It's
not your fault either. Yes, it is.</i></b></font>

862
00:36:38,238 --> 00:36:39,785
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I'm Donna.
I should have known.</i></b></font>

863
00:36:39,864 --> 00:36:43,664
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Maybe. But you always say, "Part of
being human is messing up sometimes."</i></b></font>

864
00:36:43,743 --> 00:36:46,963
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And you may be Donna,
but you're still human.</i></b></font>

865
00:36:49,249 --> 00:36:50,626
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Holy shit.</i></b></font>

866
00:36:52,585 --> 00:36:54,087
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You are ready.</i></b></font>

867
00:37:02,512 --> 00:37:05,231
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Oliver. Hey, what are you
doing in here?</i></b></font>

868
00:37:07,058 --> 00:37:08,618
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I want to know
if I was wrong about you.</i></b></font>

869
00:37:08,643 --> 00:37:09,690
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>What are you
talking about?</i></b></font>

870
00:37:09,769 --> 00:37:12,609
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I want to know if you're using this
case to get back to Pearson Specter.</i></b></font>

871
00:37:12,731 --> 00:37:14,404
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Oliver, we talked
about this.</i></b></font>

872
00:37:15,066 --> 00:37:16,826
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I thought you understood
that's not who I am.</i></b></font>

873
00:37:16,860 --> 00:37:18,487
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I thought so, too.
But then I got to thinking.</i></b></font>

874
00:37:18,570 --> 00:37:20,413
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You fooled so many people
for so long,</i></b></font>

875
00:37:20,488 --> 00:37:21,648
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>what if
you're fooling me now?</i></b></font>

876
00:37:21,990 --> 00:37:23,287
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Because you said
Pearson Specter</i></b></font>

877
00:37:23,366 --> 00:37:25,585
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>would never take on a case like
this when you were there before.</i></b></font>

878
00:37:25,660 --> 00:37:26,877
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Yeah, because they
never wanted to be</i></b></font>

879
00:37:26,953 --> 00:37:28,553
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>on the wrong side
of a corporate lawsuit.</i></b></font>

880
00:37:28,580 --> 00:37:29,957
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Then why are they on the
wrong side of one now?</i></b></font>

881
00:37:30,081 --> 00:37:32,834
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Oliver. Please. Don't
lie to me, Mike.</i></b></font>

882
00:37:33,418 --> 00:37:35,295
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Just tell me
what's going on.</i></b></font>

883
00:37:40,383 --> 00:37:42,385
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>It's a long story, but...</i></b></font>

884
00:37:43,428 --> 00:37:45,508
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>We brought the suit so that
I could get into the Bar.</i></b></font>

885
00:37:45,889 --> 00:37:48,187
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>So, you were lying to Nathan,
only not about what he thought.</i></b></font>

886
00:37:48,266 --> 00:37:49,746
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Listen to me.
I'm not going to listen.</i></b></font>

887
00:37:49,768 --> 00:37:52,049
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And you need to tell him what's going on.
I can't do that.</i></b></font>

888
00:37:52,353 --> 00:37:55,277
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And I wasn't lying to him when I said
I'm not going back to my old firm.</i></b></font>

889
00:37:55,356 --> 00:37:57,825
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I wasn't lying to him when I said
these people's lives matter to me.</i></b></font>

890
00:37:57,901 --> 00:37:59,653
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And I wasn't lying
to either one of you</i></b></font>

891
00:37:59,736 --> 00:38:02,256
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>when I said I care about what kind
of lawyer you're going to be.</i></b></font>

892
00:38:02,322 --> 00:38:04,245
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Well, if you care what kind
of lawyer I'm going to be,</i></b></font>

893
00:38:04,324 --> 00:38:06,201
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>set the right example.</i></b></font>

894
00:38:07,160 --> 00:38:09,834
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Because you owe it to Nathan
to tell him the truth.</i></b></font>

895
00:38:19,088 --> 00:38:20,385
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Hi.
Hey.</i></b></font>

896
00:38:26,387 --> 00:38:27,684
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>What's this?</i></b></font>

897
00:38:27,764 --> 00:38:30,062
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>It's every yearbook
I've ever had.</i></b></font>

898
00:38:30,558 --> 00:38:32,356
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>It was so nice doing it
with yours the other night,</i></b></font>

899
00:38:32,435 --> 00:38:34,608
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I thought maybe tonight
we could do it with mine.</i></b></font>

900
00:38:35,647 --> 00:38:37,445
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Louis, what's wrong?</i></b></font>

901
00:38:42,445 --> 00:38:44,072
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Nothing's wrong.</i></b></font>

902
00:38:45,323 --> 00:38:47,200
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I had a bad day and I wanted
to talk to you about it.</i></b></font>

903
00:38:47,283 --> 00:38:48,523
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>But you went to
all this trouble</i></b></font>

904
00:38:48,535 --> 00:38:49,536
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>and I don't want to
bring you down.</i></b></font>

905
00:38:49,619 --> 00:38:52,919
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Louis, my yearbooks
are always going to be here.</i></b></font>

906
00:38:54,082 --> 00:38:56,961
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And hearing about something as
important to you as your work</i></b></font>

907
00:38:57,043 --> 00:38:58,761
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>isn't going to
bring me down.</i></b></font>

908
00:38:58,837 --> 00:39:00,931
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>It's going to
bring us closer.</i></b></font>

909
00:39:01,005 --> 00:39:04,509
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Are you sure? Because I have
a lot of bad days at work.</i></b></font>

910
00:39:05,635 --> 00:39:07,478
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Which is all
the more reason for you</i></b></font>

911
00:39:07,554 --> 00:39:09,898
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>to have someone to make
you feel better at home.</i></b></font>

912
00:39:13,309 --> 00:39:15,482
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Okay, but it's kind of
a long story.</i></b></font>

913
00:39:16,062 --> 00:39:17,405
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Well, then you sit
right here,</i></b></font>

914
00:39:17,480 --> 00:39:20,199
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I'll go make you a drink, and then
you can tell me all about it.</i></b></font>

915
00:39:20,275 --> 00:39:22,369
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You know what
I'm in the mood for?</i></b></font>

916
00:39:22,443 --> 00:39:23,535
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I can't tell
which one yet,</i></b></font>

917
00:39:23,611 --> 00:39:27,036
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>but I'm pretty sure it's either a
Peach Schnapps or a ice cold prunie.</i></b></font>

918
00:39:27,949 --> 00:39:29,542
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You really are getting
to know me, aren't you?</i></b></font>

919
00:39:29,617 --> 00:39:31,039
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I sure am.</i></b></font>

920
00:39:41,963 --> 00:39:44,386
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Jesus Christ.
What are you doing here?</i></b></font>

921
00:39:44,966 --> 00:39:46,513
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You guys told me to
stay away from you.</i></b></font>

922
00:39:46,593 --> 00:39:49,392
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Yeah, that was before I had a chat
with your buddy, James Palmer.</i></b></font>

923
00:39:49,470 --> 00:39:51,393
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Look, I don't even know James Palmer.
So, whatever he said...</i></b></font>

924
00:39:51,472 --> 00:39:53,792
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>He didn't have to say anything.
All he had to do was point.</i></b></font>

925
00:39:57,270 --> 00:39:59,022
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>So what? This is an off-shore
account in my name.</i></b></font>

926
00:39:59,105 --> 00:40:01,608
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>An off-shore account
with $300,000 in it,</i></b></font>

927
00:40:01,691 --> 00:40:06,322
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>deposited exactly a day after Velocity
supposedly stole your technology.</i></b></font>

928
00:40:06,404 --> 00:40:08,498
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I was told by my accountant
to shelter certain earnings.</i></b></font>

929
00:40:08,573 --> 00:40:10,653
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Bullshit. You don't even
have those kind of earnings.</i></b></font>

930
00:40:10,658 --> 00:40:13,098
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And you didn't have to keep this
quiet because you're married.</i></b></font>

931
00:40:13,161 --> 00:40:15,004
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You kept it quiet
because you're in on it.</i></b></font>

932
00:40:15,580 --> 00:40:17,048
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I was in on it.</i></b></font>

933
00:40:17,123 --> 00:40:19,922
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I saw a chance to jump ship
and get paid in the process.</i></b></font>

934
00:40:20,001 --> 00:40:21,548
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>But instead,
they pulled the job</i></b></font>

935
00:40:21,628 --> 00:40:23,909
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>and put just enough money in
that account to implicate me.</i></b></font>

936
00:40:23,922 --> 00:40:25,174
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You piece of shit.</i></b></font>

937
00:40:25,298 --> 00:40:27,926
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Please. My employees are gonna
lose their jobs because of me.</i></b></font>

938
00:40:28,009 --> 00:40:31,058
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>We need to keep this suit going
and get that technology back.</i></b></font>

939
00:40:31,137 --> 00:40:32,639
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>No, buddy.</i></b></font>

940
00:40:32,722 --> 00:40:34,395
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You don't give a shit
about your employees</i></b></font>

941
00:40:34,474 --> 00:40:35,942
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>and I don't give
a shit about you.</i></b></font>

942
00:40:36,017 --> 00:40:37,457
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>This deal is done.
You can't do this.</i></b></font>

943
